---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="positive-law"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10"
>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span
                class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4 trigo-positive-chapter"
                >La Ley</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-6">El Orden del Caos</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#a8a29e] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                <ShareableQuote
                    quote="La vida salvaje es libre, pero la justicia es arbitraria (la ley del más fuerte). El trigo nos obligó a inventar la Justicia Objetiva."
                />
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/20 to-transparent rounded-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-[#1c1917] p-8 rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all duration-300"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0012 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.971zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.971z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">
                                Resolución de Conflictos
                            </h3>
                            <div
                                class="w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/50 to-transparent mb-3"
                            >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                        Cuando dos vecinos discuten por un límite de tierra, ya no se matan. Van a
                        un tercero neutral. Nacen los jueces y las leyes escritas. La violencia
                        disminuye drásticamente dentro de los muros de la ciudad.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative group">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-900/20 to-transparent rounded-lg opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-[#1c1917] p-8 rounded-lg border border-emerald-900/20 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-all duration-300"
                >
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-emerald-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke-width="1.5"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-500"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-2">
                                Derechos de Propiedad
                            </h3>
                            <div
                                class="w-12 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500/50 to-transparent mb-3"
                            >
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                        Saber que lo que siembras es tuyo permitió la inversión a largo plazo. Nadie
                        construye una casa de piedra si cree que se la quitarán mañana. La ley trajo
                        la estabilidad necesaria para el progreso.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <div
                class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-900/10 via-emerald-500/5 to-emerald-900/10 blur-xl"
            >
            </div>
            <div
                class="relative bg-[#0c0a09] border border-emerald-900/30 rounded-lg p-8 text-center"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-8 mb-4">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-500/80 mb-1">∞</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">Antes</div>
                    </div>
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-8 h-8 text-emerald-500/50"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-500 mb-1">-90%</div>
                        <div class="text-xs text-[#a8a29e] uppercase tracking-wider">Después</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs text-[#78716c] uppercase tracking-widest">
                    Reducción de Violencia Interpersonal
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
